":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1/133b86b8-9719-4360-b2e0-f2eea3052ec4","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-14T19:48:19.102Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The novelty plungers are topped by—what else—blue and red pieces.</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1#xywh=1325,164,464,229"},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1/52a4044e-2059-44fb-aa62-047bdd546d94","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-14T19:50:14.297Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p><i>Punch-Drunk Love</i> arrived at a key transitional moment—directly before cell phones. In an interview with <i>Video Store Magazine</i>, PTA noted another important technological shift: \"“[The DVD release] doesn’t affect how I would make the movie, but it certainly gets you going when you realize it’s going to be on a shelf for a lot longer than it was ever in the movie theaters [...] “It inspires me to put my best foot forward in that regard in terms of transfer, packaging, etc\" (Villa).</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1#xywh=862,424,178,139"},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1/a644bbf3-600e-4141-85a3-4a438a097f84","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-14T19:50:31.685Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Up to this point in the film, Barry’s life has been driven by his seven sisters (a fairy tale number). He is forced to walk back and forth as they call him as he can’t quite break this cycle.</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-01121/canvas/1#xywh=818,637,220,175"}]}]}]}
